{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1684-05_202","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"La Fauvette, à Sapho, arrivant de son petit Bois le 25. Avril, selon la coûtume","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mai 1684 [tome 5], p. 202-205.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Ces autres Vers, pour n’être pas adressez à Sa Majesté, ne laissent pas de loüer ce Grand Monarque. Ils sont de l’illustre Mademoiselle de Scudéry. Vous sçavez qu’elle a immortalisé les Fauvetes par le langage qu’elle leur a fait tenir. Elle a continué, &amp; voicy ce que la Fauvete de son Bois a dit cette année. Les loüanges redoublent beaucoup de prix, quand la maniere de les donner est ingénieuse.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"LA FAUVETE,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"A SAPHO,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"Arrivant à son petit Bois le 25. Avril,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[4]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"selon sa coûtume.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[6]/#"}}]}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Apres l’Hyver rigoureux,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je reviens sous cet ombrage,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le cœur toûjours amoureux,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et prest à vous rendre hommage,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Selon mon foible ramage.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais dans ces aimables Bois,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont la verdure m’enchante,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce n’est plus comme autrefois,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car l’ingénieux Acante","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne répond plus à ma voix.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Malgré son cruel silence,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis qu’il chanta mes amours,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"I’ay de la reconnoissance,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je l’admireray toûjours.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"I’ay sçeu dans ma longue course,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il n’aime plus qu’un Grand Roy,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui du Levant jusqu’à l’Ourse","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Porte l’amour, ou l’effroy,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et soûmet tout à sa Loy.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand il partit de Versailles,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je vis ce Roy sans pareil,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tel que le Dieu des Batailles,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus brillant que le Soleil.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je pensay cent fois le suivre,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au lieu de venir à vous,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et j’eusse bien voulu vivre","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aupres d’un Héros si doux.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais ayant veu la Victoire","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui voloit autour de luy,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je connus bien que la Gloire","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous l’arrachoit aujourd’huy.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je crûs oüir le Tonnerre,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je vis briller des Eclairs,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je sentis trembler la Terre,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et je craignis que la Guerre","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’allast troubler l’Univers.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’ayant pas l’aîle assez forte","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour ce rapide Guerrier,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans le zele qui m’emporte,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je reviens sur mon Meurier,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ne cesse de prier","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que bientost il nous apporte,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou l’Olive, ou le Laurier.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[6]/#"}}]}}]}}}